{"text_id":182841,"tokens":["We"," investigate"," the"," optimal"," stimulus"," and"," noise"," distributions"," for"," information"," transmission"," via"," supr","ath","reshold"," stochastic"," resonance"," in"," this"," study","."," Our"," goal"," is"," to"," identify"," the"," most"," effective"," combinations"," of"," signal"," and"," noise"," to"," enhance"," information"," transmission"," through"," bist","able"," systems","."," We"," employ"," a"," comprehensive"," framework"," combining"," analytical"," and"," numerical"," methods",","," incorporating"," the"," supr","ath","reshold"," stochastic"," resonance"," phenomenon"," to"," extract"," optimal"," input"," distributions","."," This"," framework"," allows"," us"," to"," systematically"," examine"," the"," effects"," of"," varying"," stimulus"," and"," noise"," characteristics"," on"," information"," transmission",","," quantified"," through"," the"," mutual"," information"," metric","."," Our"," motivation"," for"," this"," research"," stems"," from"," the"," growing"," need"," for"," efficient"," and"," robust"," information"," processing"," strategies"," in"," various"," fields",","," where"," noisy"," and"," sub","optimal"," conditions"," are"," common","."," Results"," show"," that"," the"," optimal"," stimulus"," and"," noise"," distributions"," exhibit"," a"," non","-","trivial"," interplay",","," where"," specific"," noise"," distributions"," can"," significantly"," enhance"," information"," transmission"," within"," certain"," ranges"," of"," stimulus"," parameters","."," Furthermore",","," our"," findings"," reveal"," that"," the"," optimal"," combinations"," exhibit"," robustness"," against"," channel"," parameter"," variability"," and"," reveal"," potential"," applications"," in"," noise","-","tolerant"," communication"," systems","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"llama3-8b","label":1}